  "name": "2 - Friday Digest Sender",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Friday Digest Sender\n\nRuns Friday evening. Pulls this week's raw promo mentions, groups them into unique senders, double-checks against Sender Preferences (safety net in case of races with Workflow 1), writes the deduped list into 'Promo Senders This Week' with a fresh uuid per sender, then sends one Telegram message per sender with Unsubscribe/Keep buttons.\n\nWorkflow 3 (Telegram Button Handler) reads the uuid back from the button tap.",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 380
      },
      "id": "d2f47145-4fc8-4257-a561-803b7a306509",
